<!DOCTYPE html>
<h2 class="page-header">Create NPC</h2>
<html>
   <head>

   </head>
   <body>
      <h4 style="color: red;">
        The only information required is the name. All other fields are optional.
     </h4>
      <form method="post" action="/NPC/create"  name="npcCreationForm" id="createNPCFORM">
         <label required for="Name">[Required. Will be displayed on NPC listing]Enter the Character's Name:</label>
         <input ng-model="Name" id="Name" name="Name" placeholder="Gandalf the Grey" required/> 
         <h2>
            Physical Description
         </h2>
         <label for="Gender">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Gender:</label>
         <input id="Gender"  type="text" name="Gender" placeholder="Male">
         <br>
         <label for="Race">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Race (human, elf, dwarf, etc.):</label>
         <input id="Race" type="text" name="Race" placeholder="Istari" list="RaceList">
         <datalist id="RaceList">
            <option>select</option>
            <option >English</option>
            <option>Tamil</option>
            <option>Telugu</option>
         </datalist>
         <br>
         <label for="Profession">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Profession or Class:</label>
         <input id="Profession" type="text" name="Profession" placeholder="Wizard">
         <br>
         <label for="Age" >[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Age:</label>
         <input id="Age" type="text" name="Age" placeholder="2019" 
         <br>
         <br>
         <label for="PDesc">Enter the Character's Physical Description:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="PDesc" type="text" name="PDesc" placeholder="He wore a tall pointed grey hat, a long grey cloak, and a silver scarf. He had a long white beard and bushy eyebrows that stuck out beyond the brim of his hat"></textarea>
         <br>
         <h2>
            Mental Description and Plot Hooks
         </h2>
         <label for="Location">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's working location and downtime locations:</label>
         <input id="Location" type="text" name="Location" placeholder="Wandering in Elf territory; Hobbit homes">
         <br>
         <label for="Drive">Enter the Character's Drives:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="Drive" type="text" name="Drive" placeholder="The Drives of a character are the character's goals, fears, core beliefs, and what they value."></textarea>
         <br>
         <label for="Hook">Enter potential plot hooks:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="Hook" type="text" name="Hook" placeholder="He's planning an expedition with Dwarves and wants the party to tag along to avoid an unluck number; He believes the party are the only ones who can destroy an Artifact of Evil"></textarea>
         <br>
         <label for="Backstory">Enter the Character's Backstory:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="Backstory" type="text" name="Backstory" placeholder="An Ishtar sent to Middle Earth to defeat Sauron with others"></textarea>
         <br>
         <h2>
            Personality
         </h2>
         <label for="persBrief">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Personality IN ONE WORD:</label>
         <input  maxlength="20" id="persBrief" type="text" name="persBrief" placeholder="Quick-tempered">
         <br>
         <label for="Personality">Enter the Character's Personality:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="Personality" type="text" name="Personality" placeholder="Keen observers of Gandalf often detected a veiled power, usually revealed in his eyes, which appeared deep and wise. He was alternately affectionate and brusque; he often surprised others with his bluntness when time was of the essence. Gandalf consistently upbraided foolish behaviour, but also richly rewarded those who acted with good intentions."></textarea>
         <br>
         <label for="Speech">Enter the Character's Speech Patterns, Mannerisms, quotes & sayings:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)" id="Speech" type="text" name="Speech" placeholder="Gandalf speaks bluntly and does not mince his words, but yet often manages to spea poetically simply because of how much he's seen in his time. 'I will not say: do not weep; for not all tears are an evil' "></textarea>
         <br>
         <h2>
            Affiliations
         </h2>
         <label for="NPCs">Enter other NPCs the Character knows and their relationship:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)"  id="NPCs" type="text" name="NPCs" placeholder="Bilbo Baggins is a Hobbit friend of Gandalf who is travelling with him."></textarea>
         <br>
         <label for="FactionType">[Will be displayed on NPC listing] Enter the Character's Faction Type</label>
         <input  maxlength="30" id="FactionType" type="text" name="FactionType" placeholder="Guardian Deities">
         <br>
         <label for="FactionDesc">Enter the Character's Faction Description:</label>
         <textarea id="FactionDesc" type="text" name="FactionDesc" placeholder="The Wizards, initially known as the Istari, were five Maiar spirits sent to Middle-earth as human forms to aid the Free Peoples against the threat of Sauron."></textarea>
         <br>
         <h2>
            Mechanics
         </h2>
         <label for="Stats">Enter the Character's Notable Stats:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)"  id="Stats" type="text" name="Stats" placeholder="Gandalf is a fighter with 18 INT with high proficiency in Use Magic Device"></textarea>
         <br>
         <label for="Items">Enter the Character's Notable Items:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)"  id="Items" type="text" name="Items" placeholder="Staff of Wizardry, Ring of Spell Storing"></textarea>
         <br>
         <h2>
           Other
        </h2>
        <label for="Other">Enter other notes that don't fit in any other category:</label>
         <textarea onkeyup="auto_grow(this)"  id="Other" type="text" name="Other"></textarea>
         <br>
        
        
         <button type="submit"  style="margin-top: 10px;" value="Send order" ng-disabled="npcCreationForm.$invalid">Submit</button>
